OL,3,CTony Blair Institute urges shift in
OL,4,Cfocus from clean to cheaper power by
OL,5,C2030
OL,7,FThe Government should switch its focus
OL,8,Ffrom clean to cheaper power by the end
OL,9,Fof the decade, Sir Tony Blair's think
OL,10,Ftank has said in the latest salvo in
OL,11,Fthe energy debate.
OL,13,FA report from the Tony Blair Institute
OL,14,F(TBI) has called on ministers to
OL,15,Fcontinue backing net zero, but re-
OL,16,Fprioritise the Government's efforts to
OL,17,Fachieve clean power by 2030 towards
OL,18,Fgrowth and value for money.
