OL,7,FAfter a row erupted earlier in the
OL,8,Fyear when the former prime minister
OL,9,Fclaimed the current climate approach
OL,10,Fwas not working, and limiting fossil
OL,11,Ffuels in the short term was "doomed to
OL,12,Ffail", the latest intervention from
OL,13,Fthe Tony Blair Institute takes care to
OL,14,Fdistance itself from anti-net zero
OL,15,Frhetoric.
