OL,7,FBut coming ahead of announcements on
OL,8,Fthe latest offshore wind contract
OL,9,Fauctions and the Government's strategy
OL,10,Ffor meeting emissions cuts targets,
OL,11,Fboth expected next week, it is likely
OL,12,Fto fuel further debate about the
OL,13,Fdirection of current energy policy.
OL,15,FIn response to the paper,
OL,16,Fenvironmental groups called for
OL,17,Fefforts to remove the UK's reliance on
OL,18,Ffossil gas which is behind much of the
OL,19,Fhigh energy costs.
