OL,7,FLabour came to power pledging "clean
OL,8,Fpower by 2030", with almost all of
OL,9,FBritain's electricity coming from
OL,10,Fclean sources such as renewables and
OL,11,Fnuclear by the end of the decade, as
OL,12,Fpart of efforts to secure energy
OL,13,Fsupplies, curb bills and tackle
OL,14,Fclimate change.
