OL,5,C2030
OL,7,FBut the agenda has faced significant
OL,8,Fpush-back from the Conservatives and
OL,9,FReform UK, who have pledged to ditch
OL,10,F"expensive" net zero policies and the
OL,11,FClimate Change Act under which targets
OL,12,Fto cut emissions to zero overall by
OL,13,F2050 are set, and maximise extraction
OL,14,Fof oil and gas from the North Sea.
OL,16,FThe TBI paper says walking back the
OL,17,FClimate Change Act or net zero targets
OL,18,F"would amount to rolling back
OL,19,Fprogress".
