OL,3,CTony Blair Institute urges shift in
OL,4,Cfocus from clean to cheaper power by
OL,5,C2030
OL,7,FBut it warns that achieving clean
OL,8,Fpower must be delivered in a way that
OL,9,Fis "cost-effective and commands public
OL,10,Fsupport", and that pushing the system
OL,11,Ftoo quickly risks driving up costs and
OL,12,Fundermining confidence.
OL,14,FIt calls for a strict cost cap for the
OL,15,Fnext round of auctions for offshore
OL,16,Fwind contracts and the introduction of
OL,17,Fzonal pricing with different
OL,18,Felectricity prices in different parts
OL,19,Fof the country ` which has already
OL,20,Fbeen ruled out by the Government.
