OL,7,FThe report also calls for efforts to
OL,8,Fcut red tape and more radical planning
OL,9,Freform to fast-track projects, and to
OL,10,Fallow developers to build clean power
OL,11,Fschemes on a "first ready, first
OL,12,Fconnected" basis.
OL,14,FThe National Energy System Operator
OL,15,F(Neso) should identify the most
OL,16,Faffordable balance of renewables,
OL,17,Fnuclear and flexible capacity, and
OL,18,Fcarbon prices should be removed from
OL,19,Fgas to cut bills, it argues.
