OL,7,FThe paper's author, TBI's energy
OL,8,Fpolicy adviser Tone Langengen, said:
OL,9,F"Launched in the middle of the gas
OL,10,Fcrisis and in a low-interest
OL,11,Fenvironment, clean power 2030 was
OL,12,Fright for its time, but circumstances
OL,13,Fhave changed ` the UK now needs more
OL,14,Fthan a decarbonisation plan, it needs
OL,15,Fa full-spectrum energy strategy built
OL,16,Fon growth, resilience and abundant
OL,17,Fclean electricity.
OL,19,F"These are not problems of the current
OL,20,FGovernment's making, but they are
OL,21,Fproblems the country must now solve."
